i gave up trying to make this map work because i was stuck for ideas and i though i was just ruining what i started, i also gave up on it as it would take a very long time to compile at the PortalFlow stage and i couldnt figure out why so i just removed the skybox to make it easier for the mapper who wants this unfinished map.

My original style of the map was goint to be a mix between Surf_Egypt & Surf_10x_final with the two side maps with you are teleported to, thought that would make fun gameplay.
